Even before I could made it inside, the young man cleaning outside greeted me, opened the door and from what I was observing once inside; he did the same for each and every passer byer. The young African American woman who took my order was very pleasant, professional and had a great memory. I say that because what I wanted wasn't restocked, (short wait)so I offered to pay then went about what I had to do. Several people entered and again she greeted everyone with a smile and kindness. She gestured that it was ready with a smile. Me thinking I  would need to repeat what I told her, no such occurrence, she had it ready and with a tray. The store was immaculately clean! And from what I gathered visually, the employees work very well together. We all hope for great service, and this is one of the best stores. The food is always consistent, never too salry or too spicey. Great Job Team Members in this Panda Express!
